ces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"900e197daae15531eb122edd8e2480f9a17b21fc","tid":1565614,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:42:42.000Z","msg":"【終極核彈】《願榮光》之後－成立海外臨時民主政府<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1566796\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1566796</a><br />\n<br />\n《願榮光》之後。。。<br />\n天滅中共 平反六四！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">海外臨時政府 自由香港<br />\nFREE HONG KONG</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/freehongkonghkg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffreehongkonghkg&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QYkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=6b168703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/freehongkonghkg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/nBMTNBB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnBMTNBB.jpg&h=16392072&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n讓這攬炒旗隨風飄揚！（logo已獲攬炒巴授權使用）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>人哋北韓都做到 香港唔係做唔到呀嘛？</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共已經決定企硬，連溫和到咁既五大訴求都唔會接受。咁呢個政府仲有咩面代表人民<br />\n<br />\n擇個好日子揀個好地方，設立海外臨時政府<br />\n<br />\n目標係「要使國際社會廣泛相信港共政府為非法政權，爭取外國政府支持，替天行道，天滅中共」<br />\n「因應警察濫用暴力+濫捕事件於國際組織上追究」<br />\n<br />\n最後「推動香港進入real autonomy 嘅時代」<br />\n<br />\n因為而家我哋已經無嘢可以好輸，如果我哋就咁俾場運動完結，最後受害，被批鬥，被清算係每一個真。香港人。前線於是，和理非也如是。警察已經將文革係各中小學重演，唔駛好耐就會到其他界別。"},{"pid":"eaac8306015f634d83e1d688e875c30a710fdf54","tid":1565614,"uid":21562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"189b3e51a395a3056e44a0f65811111afa4015d5","tid":1565614,"uid":787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:26:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GB1shJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GB1shJ.png&h=d541d59d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8uZN7iv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8uZN7iv.png&h=55d59ffe&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T21:36:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://amp.lihkg.com/thread/1642132/page\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Famp.lihkg.com%2Fthread%2F1642132%2Fpage&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QYkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=33647f58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://amp.lihkg.com/thread/1642132/page</a><br />\n點解你果個代開po會被刪？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/11/053608_a868385df7186afbfac9cb4f526100b5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F11%2F053608_a868385df7186afbfac9cb4f526100b5.png&h=db4975d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DT1dgzS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDT1dgzS.png&h=5b9ba47d&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}